title: Flight Simulator 2020  - Addon spotlight - Working Title CJ4 - version 0.12.10
description:
In this how to we are going to look at the latest version of the Working Title CJ4 addon which has been released today.

This addon replaces the default cockpit, sounds, aircraft behavior and much more for Cessna Citation CJ4 which is part of Microsoft Flight Simulator 2020.

Last week an update was already released to make this addon compatible with Sim Update VII. This latest update fixed both an issue with ILS approaches and LNAV

Working Title CJ4 can be downloaded from this site: https://github.com/Working-Title-MSFS-Mods/fspackages
